  "text": "The cBio Cancer Genomics Portal (CBioPortal) represents an important online platform for visualization and analysis of various cancer genomics data [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . CBioPortal was conducted to analyse genetic alterations of prognostic genes in HCC patients (TCGA, Provisional). Anti-cancer drugs that target these genes were also identified.",
